##IMAGE QUALITY NOTE: If you are using Avizo 2024.2 or lower you might have issues with the pixelation.  You can fix this via 
#a.	Open the Tcl Console.
#b.	Type: create HxLDAExpertSettings
#c.	Press Enter.
#d.	Enable Fixed Resolution
